<br>
Kill lots of them.<br>
<br>
With Epic + Burnt Wood Staff I can solo all the statics outside the buildings in the Bank area as well as the roamers (unless Bvellos decides to go for a walk). Each clearing gives a bit of XP (not a huge amount now that I am 61, but was decent at 60), a chance at drops for Thrug quest armors (from the Lieutenants), and a moderate amount of CoV faction.<br>
<br>
<br>
