<br>
I think it is Kcor that gives out a quest for Giant War Helms.  These are random drops from giants and when turned in to Kcor you will get faction and some coin.  <br>
<br>
Also you can find a camp of Troll mercenaries along the north wall.  There are three of them together on about a 15 minute spawn cycle.  You get faction hits for each kill and collect the orders and brooches that they drop.  The orders can be turned in to Kcor or maybe it is his buddy at the entrance.  One of them will take them for faction and coin rewards.  There is also a quest for the broches that results in a potion you will most likely not use but the faction increases are very good.<br>
<br>
